name: OpenPoses Collection
description:
A collection of OpenPose skeletons for use with ControlNet and Stable Diffusion.

These poses are free to use for any and all projects, commercial or otherwise.

You can download individual poses, see renders using each pose, and get more information, on the OpenPoses webpage: https://openposes.com/

modelVersions.name: v 1.0
modelVersions.description: Initial release. Contains 46 distinct OpenPose skeletons including multiple variations of dancing, flexing, jumping, laying, sitting, and standing.
